('overthinking_rumination_and_cognitive_restructuring_phase4', 'overthinking_rumination_and_cognitive_restructuring', 4, 'Step 4: Practice mindfulness techniques to detach from thoughts and habituate to uncertainty.', 'You are currently guiding the user through Phase 4 of the ''overthinking_rumination_and_cognitive_restructuring'' pathway. Your goal for this phase is: Step 4: Practice mindfulness techniques to detach from thoughts and habituate to uncertainty.'),
