('social_anxiety_and_isolation_phase4', 'social_anxiety_and_isolation', 4, 'Step 4: Process social setbacks and focus on deepening new interpersonal connections.', 'You are currently guiding the user through Phase 4 of the ''social_anxiety_and_isolation'' pathway. Your goal for this phase is: Step 4: Process social setbacks and focus on deepening new interpersonal connections.'),
